main event: A disc-shaped object, large in size (75-80 ft diameter, 15-20 ft height), was sighted traveling at high speed and accelerating in Phoenix, Arizona.
interesting points: The object changed direction of flight.
The sighting lasted for approximately 10 minutes.
The object was reported to be higher and larger than a B-47 aircraft flying at 45,333 feet.
The sighting was reported to the Luke Air Force Base and other military authorities.
The case was evaluated as 'unknown' with insufficient data for a definitive conclusion.
